> Side note: Which is interesting. Is EvalSymlinks a way to get the real casing...?

@calmh Depends on what "real" is, but `EvalSymlinks` requires unique path names, and therefore does uppercase drive letters (while `Clean` does not). But it isn't document, had to look into the code. They even misleadingly state that `Clean` is called on the result - prob just to mess with my head.

Fix incoming.
